node.text: 😆📘 Excited to share the FINAL cover for #ComingUpForAir, coming out 14th October. It’s been a privilege to reflect back on my whole life so far while writing this… it’s been an amazing journey, not without its challenges both professionally and personally but I’m so grateful for the highs, the lessons I’ve learned from the lows and how all of those experiences have shaped who I am today. And my hopes for the future… link in my bio if you want to take a look… and it has been said, I look great on a shelf 😂
